				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%93i-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C6%B0u-h%E1%BA%ADu-Hu%E1%BB%87-Ngh%C4%A9a-t%E1%BB%B1-ti%E1%BB%85n-Gia-Ch%C3%A2u-Th%C3%B4i-%C4%91%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-ph%C3%B3-ch%C3%A2u/poem-Y3ikQV-ezmxSYnUDxlKA8A">Bồi Chương lưu hậu Huệ Nghĩa tự, tiễn Gia Châu Thôi đô đốc phó châu - 陪章留後惠義寺餞嘉州崔都督赴州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Chi%E1%BA%BFt-h%E1%BA%A1m-tinh-tr%E1%BB%B1c-th%E1%BA%A7n/poem-CXhS00MnAwXRdhJRz9LKGA">Chiết hạm tinh trực thần - 折檻旌直臣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/Cung-th%E1%BB%A9-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-ho%E1%BA%A1-Ch%E1%BA%BF-%C4%91%C3%A0i-Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-neQeLWKFXtyvE3yUO1c38g">Cung thứ Trần đại nhân hoạ Chế đài Hoàng đại nhân nguyên vận - 恭次陳大人和制臺黃大人原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Du-Th%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90inh-s%C6%A1n/poem-pJAWo0CNtnx6Y8n62FZrxg">Du Thần Đinh sơn - 遊神丁山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/D%E1%BB%AF-thi-h%E1%BB%AFu-Phan-Long-Tr%C3%A2n-du-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1c-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A2n/poem-c66Lkci6txOArDMiGj9TPw">Dữ thi hữu Phan Long Trân du Côn Sơn nhân tác Côn Sơn hành vân - 與詩友潘龍珍遊崑山因作崑山行云</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/Mi%C3%AAu-chi-t%C3%A1n/poem-MpdfZJ5EEas7IHXfCBCbBQ">Miêu chi tán - 貓之贊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/author-o7Hf6CJEKu5UA5pXP2ZmbA">Nguyễn Hữu Thăng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%B1-kinh-ph%C3%B3-Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-Ti%C3%AAn-huy%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C5%A9-b%C3%A1ch-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-qHlDll4qtUH2nCJy2-kR4Q">Tự kinh phó Phụng Tiên huyện vịnh hoài ngũ bách tự - 自京赴奉先縣詠懷五百字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/%E1%BB%A8c-giang-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-MgND7s9T1CbFzqVYlJJ7hg">Ức giang liễu - 憶江柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-n%E1%BB%99i-nh%C3%A2n-tr%C3%BA-mi%C3%AAn/poem-6vKILfvKtjsKn3_B5cMJvw">Vịnh nội nhân trú miên - 詠內人晝眠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%C3%AAu-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-vVug93Sf3-jdm37KhWEtiw">Tiêu Cương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Kh%C3%B4i/Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%81ng-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-esupLHIYESSVN7lYbvHxGQ">Xuân Áng tức cảnh kỳ 1 - 春盎即景其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Kh%C3%B4i/author-tgqd0ci_mcXuakVjLSEWmg">Phan Khôi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
